- The pipeline runs static checks and Linux Docker-based builds.
- It produces deb packages, Python wheels, and Docker images.
- Then runs a test matrix including smoke tests on physical hardware and the TTSim simulator to verify correctness and performance.
- Incremental and full clang-tidy runs ensure code quality.

